{"tid":648413,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【直播雙人爆機】唯一出口《A Way Out》情願中子彈 唔再執番梘！","createTime":"2018-04-30T16:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T20:39:26.000Z","uid":93870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4576b2c7ad560576a161c295bbd03691640e0be7","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>按此進入Twitch直播：</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/smilesnooker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fsmilesnooker&d=CKP6R7xOsIMcEqWMGR%2ByKJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4f060c07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/smilesnooker</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>00:00 - 01:00《沙填入臀門股東大會》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>深夜 01:00 《A Way Out》正式開始！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/awpyi8zm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fawpyi8zm&h=bebcc7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《A Way Out》是限定雙人合作的冒險遊戲，玩家可以各自扮演兩名囚犯之一，展開大膽的越獄行動。<br />\n<br />\n本作跳脫以往遊戲的框架，將從一開始的刺激逃獄行動，迅速演變為充滿變數和革命情感的冒險。 <br />\n<br />\n玩家可以操控兩名主角&ndash;里歐 (Leo) 和文森 (Vincent)，為了越獄重獲自由而迫不得已攜手合作。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s9xea2mv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs9xea2mv&h=9f35fdaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3wcsyqbp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3wcsyqbp&h=27895535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ro94hwva\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fro94hwva&h=aa2727c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我係 L仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚會同 沙填入臀門 巴打一齊逃出生天！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴打入黎邊傾邊睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家踴躍發言！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚，我哋情願中子彈，唔再執番梘！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>按此進入Twitch直播：</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/smilesnooker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fsmilesnooker&d=CKP6R7xOsIMcEqWMGR%2ByKJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=07ba9cd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/smilesnooker</a></span>"},{"pid":"ecf83b683c0bde1ee87786c6d538af806572aa29","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f9135d9a1b32c953e6489e05a1da9db2cca6b5","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T19:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbc0903b41ca292f1a3c22d636d8d498bcffd61","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T19:31:01.000Z","msg":"各位巴打踴躍發言！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada42cdbffa586a4b34d559a5f4af0cae03a53d4","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T19:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247eefe60669c171c1ee74cc1c4a3e77a9fe405f","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T19:33:26.000Z","msg":"各位巴打踴躍發言！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10031335043798e31d5af841914075aab48a092","tid":648413,"uid":93870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime